  "claim": {
    "id": "CLM-32",
    "text": "FaMe trade s.r.o. (IČO 29292859, founded 2011) is ACTIVE, and Václav Faraga currently holds 50 % (since 14 Dec 2020) and remains a jednatel, alongside Tomáš Melichárek (50 %, jednatel). Petr Faraga was a jednatel and shareholder until December 2020. Melichárek's 50 % record shows the same Jan–Apr 2026 re-registration churn as his other holdings.",
    "status": "VERIFIED_PRIMARY",
    "note": "CORRECTION of the earlier mirror-based record, which stated the company was dissolved/exited and that both Václav and Petr Faraga had left by end-2020 — the primary register contradicts that for Václav Faraga, who took 50 % at exactly that date.",
    "sources": [
      "SRC-12"
    ]
  },
